  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">On pages 1-2 of this letter, Charlotte Austin Joy gives a list of items sent from Nantucket to the Massachusetts Anti-Slavery Fair, with their prices. The net proceeds from the Nantucket anti-slavery fair were about $175. After the close of the fair, they had a &quot;miniature soiree,&quot; which brought in $25. The items sent were leftover from the Nantucket fair.</subfield>
